cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.NI 

The paper deals with defending against attacks on position sensors, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of machine learning in one of the proposed defenses also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The implementation of the defenses on smartphones and IoT sensor nodes indicates a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
